  "details": "A security vulnerability has been detected in youlaitech youlai-boot up to 2.21.1. This affects the function getUserList of the file src/main/java/com/youlai/boot/system/controller/UserController.java of the component Users Endpoint. Such manipulation of the argument order leads to sql injection. The attack may be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed publicly and may be used. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure but did not respond in any way.",
